Changing Your Password

You can change your password at any time directly in Nextcloud:
"Settings" > "Security" > "Change password"

Make sure the email address in your profile is up to date so you can reset your password if needed.
Managing Your Storage

You can check your current storage usage at any time:
- In Nextcloud: Bottom left of the sidebar
- In the client area: "Services" > "{$service_product_name}"

Need more storage? You can upgrade your plan at any time through the client area.
